### HTTP Request
`POST /v3/sales_reps`

**Parameters**

| Name | Located in | Description | Required | Type |
| ---- | ---------- | ----------- | -------- | ---- |
| `organizationId` | body | Organization ID | Yes | `integer` |
| `salesRep` | body | Sales Rep Record | Yes | `json` |

**Sales Rep Parameters**

| Name | Located in | Description | Required | Type | Value |
| ---- | ---------- | ----------- | -------- | ---- | ----- |
| `firstName` | salesRep | Sales rep first name | Yes | `string` ||
| `lastName` | salesRep | Sales rep last name | Yes | `string` ||
| `email` | salesRep | Sales rep email | Yes | `string` ||
| `salesGroupId` | salesRep | Sales group ID | No | `integer` ||
| `hasRequisitionAccess` | salesRep | Mark as true if sales rep has access to requisition information | No | boolean | `true`,`false` |
| `officePhoneNumber` | salesRep | Office phone number of sales rep | No | `string` ||

**Responses**

| Code | Description |
| ---- | ----------- |
| 200 | Created Sales Rep Record |

